## Per-env local.properties template — KC-3 / Phase 2.8.B
##
## Copy to `local.properties` and uncomment the env block matching the
## release build you're producing. The values below are also valid as
## CI env vars (Gradle reads from both — see `app/build.gradle.kts`).
## See `docs/keycloak-implementation-gaps.md` Phase 2.8.B for the
## TestFlight / Play Console release recipe.

## REQUIRED for any build — points Gradle at your local Android SDK.
## sdk.dir=/Users/<you>/Library/Android/sdk

## --- Local docker-compose dev (default for engineering) -----------
## Pointed at the Android emulator's host loopback. SSO ON.
## KEYCLOAK_SSO_ENABLED=true
## KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=http://10.0.2.2:8081/realms/hms
## KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID=hms-patient-android
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_SCHEME=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_URI=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient:/oauth2redirect

## --- Release-Dev (`hms-keycloak-dev` Railway service) -------------
## Internal Testing track, SSO ON for QA against the dev Railway realm.
## KEYCLOAK_SSO_ENABLED=true
## KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=https://hms-keycloak-dev.up.railway.app/realms/hms
## KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID=hms-patient-android
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_SCHEME=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_URI=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient:/oauth2redirect

## --- Release-UAT (`hms-keycloak-uat` Railway service) -------------
## Internal Testing UAT track, SSO ON for the pre-cutover soak.
## KEYCLOAK_SSO_ENABLED=true
## KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=https://hms-keycloak-uat.up.railway.app/realms/hms
## KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID=hms-patient-android
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_SCHEME=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_URI=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient:/oauth2redirect

## --- Release-Prod (`hms-keycloak-prod` Railway service) -----------
## Production track. SSO stays OFF until Phase 3 cutover (see
## docs/keycloak-implementation-gaps.md Phase 2.8.C). The issuer URL
## is pre-staged so the cutover flip is one local.properties line,
## not a code edit.
## KEYCLOAK_SSO_ENABLED=false
## KEYCLOAK_ISSUER=https://hms-keycloak-prod.up.railway.app/realms/hms
## KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID=hms-patient-android
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_SCHEME=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient
## KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_URI=com.bitnesttechs.hms.patient:/oauth2redirect

## --- Release signing (required for `bundleRelease`) ---------------
## STORE_FILE=../upload-keystore.jks
## STORE_PASSWORD=<keystore password>
## KEY_ALIAS=upload
## KEY_PASSWORD=<key password>
